						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AA Canadian University’s Curious Connection to the Titan Submersible Disaster%0D%0AThe Marine Institute at Memorial University in Newfoundland and Labrador partnered with OceanGate—but why?%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/features/a-canadian-universitys-curious-connection-to-the-titan-submersible-disaster/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



